Harikrishna, Pentala (2711) - Ivanchuk, Vasyl (2664)
Polish Ekstraliga (chess24.com) [5] 2023.09.22
D10 Queen's Gambit Declined Slav defence

1.d4 d5 2.c4 c6 3.Nc3 Nf6 4.cxd5 cxd5 5.Bf4 Nc6 6.e3 a6 7.Be2 Bf5 8.Nf3 e6 9.Qb3 Ra7 10.Ne5 Nxe5 11.Bxe5 Nd7 12.O-O b5 13.Rfd1 Qa8 14.Rac1 Nxe5 15.dxe5 Be7 16.Nxb5 axb5 17.Bxb5+ Kf8 18.Bc6

00:00 Hello Everyone!

The 2023 Polish Ekstraliga is a 10-team round-robin from 18-26 September in Lublin.

Each match is played on six boards, with teams required to play a female player on board 6. The time control is 90 minutes for 40 moves then 30 minutes to the end of the game, with a 30-second increment from move 1. Official website: pzszach.pl
